Metadata for annual key measures and variables

Source: vignettes/metadata-annual.Rmd
metadata-annual.Rmd

Note: This package currently only provides metadata for the most recent annual reporting period.

key_measures measures

Column Description
OrgType The type of organisation to which the data refer. Data are published for the following organisation types: - England (aggregated data for all NHS Talking Therapies service providers) - Commissioning Region - Integrated Care Board (ICB) - Subsection of Integrated Care Board (SubICB) - NHS Talking Therapies service provider
OrgCode The Organisation Data Service (ODS) code of the organisation to which the data refer. Data are published for the following organisation types: - England (aggregated data for all NHS Talking Therapies service providers) - Commissioning Region - Integrated Care Board (ICB) - Subsection of Integrated Care Board (SubICB) - NHS Talking Therapies service provider
OrgName The Organisation Data Service (ODS) name of the organisation to which the data refer. Data are published for the following organisation types: - England (aggregated data for all NHS Talking Therapies service providers) - Commissioning Region - Integrated Care Board (ICB) - Subsection of Integrated Care Board (SubICB) - NHS Talking Therapies service provider
VariableType The type of variable by which the data are categorised. See Derivations tab of this file for full details. The following variables are used: - Total - Age Group - Age Group / Gender - Consultation Medium - Disability - Ethnic Group - Ethnic Group / Gender - Ex-British Armed Forces and Dependants - Gender - Indices of Deprivation Decile - Long Term Condition Status - Mental Health Care Cluster - Problem Descriptor - Religion - Sexual Orientation - Stepped Care Pathway - Waiting Time
VariableA The high-level variable values for the categories described in VariableType.
VariableB The sub-category (where applicable - NULL if not applicable) variable values for the categories described in VariableType.
Count_ReferralsReceived Count of referrals with a referral request received date in the year.
Count_AccessingServices Count of referrals with a first attended treatment appointment (accessed services) in the year.
Count_SecondTreatment Count of referrals with a second treatment appointment in the year
Count_FinishedCourseTreatment Count of referrals with an end date in the year that had at least two attended treatment appointments (excluding follow up).
Percentage_FinishedCourseTreatment The proportion of all referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and at least two attended treatment appointments excluding follow up) for the specified organisation having the specified variableA and variableB values. Expressed as a percentage.
Count_EndedReferrals Count of referrals with an end date in the year.
Count_EndedBeforeTreatment Count of referrals with an end date in the year that had no treatment appointments or internet therapy logs recorded.
Count_EndedAfterOneTreatment Count of referrals with an end date in the year that had only one treatment appointment or internet therapy log recorded.
Mean_ApptsFinishedCourseTreatment Mean number of treatment appointments for referrals with an end date in the year that had at least two attended treatment appointments (excluding follow up) and have finished a course of treatment.
Mean_WaitAccessingServices Mean waiting time in days between the referral request received date and the date of first therapeutic appointment, where the referral had a first attended treatment appointment (accessing services) in the year.
Mean_WaitCompletedTreatment Mean waiting time in days between the referral request received date and the date of the first therapeutic appointment, where the referral finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and having a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral).
Count_AppropriatePairedADSM Count of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and having a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) and had paired scores on the specified Anxiety Disorder Specific Measure (ADSM).
Percentage_AppropriatePairedADSM Proportion of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and having a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) and had paired scores on the specified Anxiety Disorder Specific Measure (ADSM).
Count_AtCaseness Count of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and having a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) where the service user was at caseness at initial assessment.
Count_NotAtCaseness Count of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and having a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) where the service user was not at caseness at initial assessment.
Count_Improvement Count of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and having a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) where the service user showed reliable improvement.
Percentage_Improvement Proportion of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) that showed reliable improvement, expressed as a percentage.
Count_NoReliableChange Count of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) that show no reliable change.
Percentage_NoReliableChange Proportion of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) that show no reliable change, expressed as a percentage.
Count_Deterioration Count of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) that show reliable deterioration.
Percentage_Deterioration Proportion of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) that show reliable deterioration, expressed as a percentage.
Count_Recovery Count of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) where the service user has moved to recovery.
Percentage_Recovery Proportion of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) where the service user has moved to recovery, expressed as a percentage.
Count_ReliableRecovery Count of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) where the service user showed reliable recovery (has moved to recovery and showed reliable improvement).
Percentage_ReliableRecovery Proportion of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) that showed reliable recovery (has moved to recovery and showed reliable improvement), expressed as a percentage.
Count_BAFIndicatorCompletion Count of referrals received in the year where the ex-British Armed Forces Indicator has been validly completed.
Percentage_BAFIndicatorCompletion Proportion of referrals received in the year where the ex-British Armed Forces Indicator has been validly completed, expressed as a percentage.
Count_FinishedTreatmentFirst6Months Count of referrals that finished a course of treatment in the first six months of the year (end date between 1st April 2021 and 30th September 2021 and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral)
Count_FinishedTreatmentFirst6MonthsFollowUp Count of referrals that finished a course of treatment in the first six months of the year (end date between 1st April 2021 and 30th September 2021 and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) had one or more follow-up appointments at least 30 days after the referral end date.
Percentage_FollowUpAppointment Proportion of referrals that finished a course of treatment in the first six months of the year (end date between 1st April 2021 and 30th September 2021 and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) had one or more follow-up appointments at least 30 days after the referral end date, expressed as a percentage.
Mean_ContactDuration The mean duration (in minutes) of NHS Talking Therapies treatment appointments for referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral).
Median_ContactDuration The median duration (in minutes) of NHS Talking Therapies treatment appointments for referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral).
Sum_ContactDuration The total duration (in minutes) of all NHS Talking Therapies treatment appointments for referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral). Numerator for MeanTotalContactDurationPerReferral.
Mean_TotalContactDurationPerReferral The mean total duration (in minutes) of all NHS Talking Therapies treatment appointments for referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral).
Median_TotalContactDurationPerReferral The median total duration (in minutes) of all NHS Talking Therapies treatment appointments for referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral).
Count_FinishedCourseTreatmentContactDuration The count of referrals that finished a course of treatment (end date in the year and a minimum of two attended treatment appointments during the referral) having at least one appointment with a contact duration greater than zero minutes. Denominator for MeanTotalContactDurationPerReferral.
Mean_TreatmentAppointmentsRecovery Mean number of treatment appointments for referrals with an end date in the year that had at least two attended treatment appointments (excluding follow up) and have finished a course of treatment and moved to recovery.
Mean_TreatmentAppointmentsImprovement Mean number of treatment appointments for referrals with an end date in the year that had at least two attended treatment appointments (excluding follow up) and have finished a course of treatment and showed reliable improvement.
Mean_TreatmentAppointmentsNoChange Mean number of treatment appointments for referrals with an end date in the year that had at least two attended treatment appointments (excluding follow up) and have finished a course of treatment and showed no reliable change.
Mean_TreatmentAppointmentsDeterioration Mean number of treatment appointments for referrals with an end date in the year that had at least two attended treatment appointments (excluding follow up) and have finished a course of treatment and showed reliable deterioration.
Mean_TreatmentAppointmentsReliableRecovery Mean number of treatment appointments for referrals with an end date in the year that had at least two attended treatment appointments (excluding follow up) and have finished a course of treatment and moved to reliable recovery.
